headline: Donny Osmond Extends Residency at Harrah’s Las Vegas
summary: LAS VEGAS, March 13, 2025--Legendary entertainer and music icon Donny Osmond proudly announces the extension to his award-winning residency inside Harrah’s Showroom at Harrah’s Las Vegas through November 2025.
